episodes.title: Ex Carbon Nation Member Speak Out Against Nature Boy AKA Eligio Bishop (Cult Leader ARRESTED)
episodes.description:
Today we take a look at Nature Boy AKA Eligio Bishop and his disturbing cult. We discuss the terrible things he has done and also listen to a few ex members stories. This cult leader was finally arrested April 2024 and despite all his wrong doing still has a following. Today we shed light on this person to help current members realize the dangers of his group and prevent others from finding their way into a situation like this? So what are your thoughts on this situation?
